{
  "stem": "4361.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think, I think it was the best education I ever got because what also happened after numerous clauses was introduced, they also fired all the Jewish professors who taught at-- in Hungarian universities.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had the best of the best among the educators teaching us, teaching high school students.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was sent to Kolozsvar for my studies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How was that for you to be so involved in your first high school and suddenly have to stop and change and leave home?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, it was terrible, but it was also an adventure because it was the first time that I was going away from home.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I felt sort of rather confident because I was an A student all around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And although I heard that this is a very special school and you really have to be very, very good, I figured, well, I was a first-- you know, I was-- I always got prizes and so I'll have no problem.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't really have a problem when I went to school, except that everybody else there was an A student, you see, because they were really-- they-- they had to limit the number of the students they were taking.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was not good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The thing that made it easier for me was that one of my friends-- her name is Susanna Glazinger, I remember-- she also was accepted.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the two of us-- my mother came with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she took-- she made sure that we are going to stay with somebody very appropriate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that somebody very appropriate was nobody less than the chairman of the board of the Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the girls were in good hands.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
